1
00:00:11,796 --> 00:00:14,600
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:17,189
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:17,856 --> 00:00:21,264
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:22,961 --> 00:00:25,968
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:26,343 --> 00:00:28,867
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:29,211 --> 00:00:32,646
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:39,620
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:40,302 --> 00:00:45,384
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:46,176 --> 00:00:48,672
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:48,672 --> 00:00:51,280
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:51,796 --> 00:00:59,061
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:01:00,032 --> 00:01:02,788
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:01:02,848 --> 00:01:05,688
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:01:05,981 --> 00:01:07,008
♪Let me♪

15
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:11,283
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:11,733 --> 00:01:14,412
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:14,696 --> 00:01:17,397
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:17,568 --> 00:01:19,038
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:19,038 --> 00:01:23,214
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:23,565 --> 00:01:33,824
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:35,251 --> 00:01:40,800
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,944
=Episode 26=

23
00:01:42,995 --> 00:01:43,835
Come on.

24
00:01:45,915 --> 00:01:46,755
Thank you.

25
00:01:47,594 --> 00:01:48,434
Thank you.

26
00:01:49,314 --> 00:01:50,154
Take your time.

27
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,275
(This is)

28
00:01:51,275 --> 00:01:52,635
(tragic reality in this city.)

29
00:01:53,554 --> 00:01:54,394
(It seems we must)

30
00:01:54,394 --> 00:01:55,594
(think of an idea quickly)

31
00:01:55,995 --> 00:01:56,835
(to repel the Wutuo.)

32
00:01:56,835 --> 00:01:57,675
Is this enough?

33
00:01:59,195 --> 00:02:00,035
General Wu'an,

34
00:02:00,755 --> 00:02:01,635
the congee is shared.

35
00:02:02,555 --> 00:02:03,595
By the way, Ms. Qi Luo,

36
00:02:04,394 --> 00:02:05,355
didn't we send people

37
00:02:05,435 --> 00:02:07,355
to inform their families
to pick them up?

38
00:02:07,635 --> 00:02:09,714
Why hasn't anyone returned home?

39
00:02:09,954 --> 00:02:11,035
They were abducted

40
00:02:11,635 --> 00:02:12,514
and violated.

41
00:02:13,155 --> 00:02:15,274
Their families think they're a disgrace,

42
00:02:16,274 --> 00:02:17,514
refusing to take them back.

43
00:02:18,954 --> 00:02:20,794
This calamity wasn't their choice.

44
00:02:21,554 --> 00:02:23,075
They've narrowly escaped death,

45
00:02:23,475 --> 00:02:24,755
but their families bar the door.

46
00:02:25,554 --> 00:02:26,875
How ridiculous.

47
00:02:27,475 --> 00:02:28,755
If they were men,

48
00:02:29,514 --> 00:02:30,435
they'd already be home

49
00:02:30,755 --> 00:02:31,954
with their families.

50
00:02:32,355 --> 00:02:34,794
Maybe even praised as heroes.

51
00:02:35,595 --> 00:02:36,915
How could that be heroic?

52
00:02:37,274 --> 00:02:38,155
True heroes like you.

53
00:02:38,432 --> 00:02:39,635
Protecting homes and citizens.

54
00:02:40,114 --> 00:02:40,994
That's real heroism.

55
00:02:42,075 --> 00:02:42,915
And my master.

56
00:02:43,234 --> 00:02:44,274
You two

57
00:02:44,274 --> 00:02:46,554
are both great heroes
defending Wei's people.

58
00:02:49,114 --> 00:02:50,595
I won't claim to be a hero.

59
00:02:51,355 --> 00:02:52,195
As for Li Kuang,

60
00:02:53,504 --> 00:02:55,035
heroes don't follow the crowd

61
00:02:55,435 --> 00:02:58,435
or push suffering people
deeper into despair.

62
00:02:59,035 --> 00:03:00,475
Nor would they save rations

63
00:03:00,875 --> 00:03:03,514
by starving those they should protect.

64
00:03:04,075 --> 00:03:06,114
Are you blaming my master?

65
00:03:06,674 --> 00:03:08,394
He has his difficulties.

66
00:03:08,755 --> 00:03:10,234
The city's food reserves are low.

67
00:03:10,435 --> 00:03:11,755
He's deeply concerned.

68
00:03:11,954 --> 00:03:12,794
So...

69
00:03:14,155 --> 00:03:14,995
Ms. Qi Luo,

70
00:03:15,155 --> 00:03:15,995
are you alright?

71
00:03:16,514 --> 00:03:17,514
I have some ointment.

72
00:03:17,755 --> 00:03:18,595
I'll get it for you.

73
00:03:18,674 --> 00:03:20,875
These minor injuries are nothing.

74
00:03:21,315 --> 00:03:22,355
Don't blame my master.

75
00:03:22,834 --> 00:03:24,195
He's actually kind-hearted.

76
00:03:24,994 --> 00:03:26,755
He saved me from street thugs

77
00:03:27,274 --> 00:03:28,274
and gave me food

78
00:03:28,994 --> 00:03:30,755
and shelter.

79
00:03:31,195 --> 00:03:32,075
Ms. Qi Luo,

80
00:03:33,075 --> 00:03:34,195
is this what 'good' means?

81
00:03:34,875 --> 00:03:35,715
He married you.

82
00:03:35,834 --> 00:03:37,755
Shouldn't he care for you?

83
00:03:38,435 --> 00:03:39,674
In these chaotic times,

84
00:03:39,875 --> 00:03:40,915
as a woman,

85
00:03:41,435 --> 00:03:42,394
I belong to him.

86
00:03:42,674 --> 00:03:44,915
It's my duty to serve him well,

87
00:03:45,475 --> 00:03:47,155
respect him, obey him,

88
00:03:47,394 --> 00:03:48,674
and make him my universe.

89
00:03:48,875 --> 00:03:49,715
Slow down.

90
00:03:50,114 --> 00:03:50,954
Be careful.

91
00:03:52,475 --> 00:03:53,315
Is this better?

92
00:03:58,475 --> 00:03:59,315
Master.

93
00:04:00,114 --> 00:04:01,075
I'm scared.

94
00:04:01,755 --> 00:04:03,075
I don't want to go.

95
00:04:04,114 --> 00:04:05,794
I only want to stay with you.

96
00:04:05,875 --> 00:04:07,755
I don't want to be anyone's example.

97
00:04:10,155 --> 00:04:12,034
Rundu must not fall to Wutuo.

98
00:04:12,834 --> 00:04:14,354
As Rundu's defender,

99
00:04:15,354 --> 00:04:17,315
I'll protect it even
at the cost of my life.

100
00:04:18,594 --> 00:04:20,354
But with our current forces,

101
00:04:20,594 --> 00:04:21,834
we stand no chance.

102
00:04:22,154 --> 00:04:23,235
We must burn our boats

103
00:04:23,354 --> 00:04:24,194
and fight them

104
00:04:24,195 --> 00:04:25,115
to the bitter end!

105
00:04:26,075 --> 00:04:27,994
You and those female captives
are vanguards.

106
00:04:28,235 --> 00:04:30,154
After you distract the Wutuo forces,

107
00:04:31,034 --> 00:04:32,235
I'll lead the army to battle

108
00:04:32,914 --> 00:04:34,235
and die defending Rundu.

109
00:04:45,235 --> 00:04:46,315
I understand now.

110
00:04:52,354 --> 00:04:53,514
I'll go.

111
00:04:56,195 --> 00:04:57,555
Please take care.

112
00:05:00,755 --> 00:05:02,154
He, He.

113
00:05:04,155 --> 00:05:05,834
Mai and I heard something

114
00:05:05,834 --> 00:05:06,674
on our way here.

115
00:05:06,994 --> 00:05:07,834
Li Kuang

116
00:05:07,834 --> 00:05:09,248
plans to send the women we rescued

117
00:05:09,248 --> 00:05:10,795
to the battlefield

118
00:05:10,795 --> 00:05:11,875
to fight the enemies!

119
00:05:13,914 --> 00:05:15,514
He's sending them to die!

120
00:05:19,954 --> 00:05:20,794
Let's go.

121
00:05:40,115 --> 00:05:41,154
Tainted by the enemy.

122
00:05:42,034 --> 00:05:43,154
Disgrace to the family.

123
00:05:44,834 --> 00:05:45,834
Not worthy to live.

124
00:05:47,474 --> 00:05:48,394
Not worthy to live.

125
00:05:58,034 --> 00:05:58,874
Mr. Wang,

126
00:05:59,315 --> 00:06:00,474
as the Military Director,

127
00:06:00,914 --> 00:06:02,154
I can command you.

128
00:06:03,034 --> 00:06:03,874
By my order,

129
00:06:04,235 --> 00:06:05,075
do not open the gate.

130
00:06:06,795 --> 00:06:07,635
Mr. Chu.

131
00:06:07,995 --> 00:06:09,435
All hangs on this move.

132
00:06:09,875 --> 00:06:12,115
But I serve Rundu's garrison.

133
00:06:12,755 --> 00:06:14,394
We only obey Commander Li's orders.

134
00:06:15,954 --> 00:06:16,794
Open the gate.

135
00:06:18,995 --> 00:06:19,835
Mr. Wang!

136
00:06:24,274 --> 00:06:25,354
Open the gate!

137
00:07:03,594 --> 00:07:04,795
Let me see who will open it!

138
00:07:05,315 --> 00:07:06,755
This is Rundu.

139
00:07:07,075 --> 00:07:09,034
I'm General Wu'an
appointed by His Majesty.

140
00:07:09,635 --> 00:07:10,914
Not under your jurisdiction.

141
00:07:12,674 --> 00:07:14,354
I'm not your soldier.

142
00:07:24,514 --> 00:07:25,354
Lure the enemy?

143
00:07:26,034 --> 00:07:26,874
Commander Li.

144
00:07:27,034 --> 00:07:28,394
You're just sacrificing lives.

145
00:07:29,195 --> 00:07:30,035
General Wu'an.

146
00:07:30,354 --> 00:07:31,635
Your contributions to Rundu

147
00:07:31,954 --> 00:07:33,235
are deeply appreciated.

148
00:07:33,755 --> 00:07:34,635
But even so,

149
00:07:34,795 --> 00:07:36,595
you can't interfere in
our military affairs.

150
00:07:37,435 --> 00:07:39,315
If you overstep again,

151
00:07:39,755 --> 00:07:40,595
just leave Rundu.

152
00:07:40,754 --> 00:07:42,434
You're the one who should leave!

153
00:07:44,995 --> 00:07:45,875
Please calm down.

154
00:07:48,514 --> 00:07:49,675
Don't blame Commander Li.

155
00:07:50,394 --> 00:07:51,234
We

156
00:07:51,675 --> 00:07:52,594
volunteered.

157
00:07:53,795 --> 00:07:54,635
We are

158
00:07:54,834 --> 00:07:56,274
defiled.

159
00:07:57,075 --> 00:07:58,635
No dignity to keep living.

160
00:08:00,235 --> 00:08:01,435
If our deaths

161
00:08:02,034 --> 00:08:03,514
can gain Rundu an advantage,

162
00:08:03,795 --> 00:08:05,834
we'll cleanse our shame

163
00:08:06,315 --> 00:08:07,594
and die with honor.

164
00:08:08,195 --> 00:08:09,954
Commander Li
entrusted us with this task.

165
00:08:10,354 --> 00:08:11,514
He's giving us chances.

166
00:08:12,875 --> 00:08:13,715
If we can

167
00:08:14,274 --> 00:08:15,474
deceive the Wutuo enemies

168
00:08:15,915 --> 00:08:16,755
and make them believe

169
00:08:16,755 --> 00:08:17,995
Rundu has no fighters left,

170
00:08:18,474 --> 00:08:20,115
we'll gain an advantage

171
00:08:20,514 --> 00:08:21,354
and strike them

172
00:08:21,354 --> 00:08:22,474
unprepared at the showdown.

173
00:08:22,914 --> 00:08:23,754
Chances?

174
00:08:24,315 --> 00:08:25,795
So I'm blocking your way to merit?

175
00:08:29,634 --> 00:08:30,474
Yes.

176
00:08:31,195 --> 00:08:32,114
In crisis,

177
00:08:32,915 --> 00:08:34,435
we should unite

178
00:08:34,634 --> 00:08:35,555
against foes.

179
00:08:35,754 --> 00:08:38,035
But not by sending you
to die pointlessly.

180
00:08:38,515 --> 00:08:39,675
This isn't courage.

181
00:08:40,114 --> 00:08:40,994
This is foolishness.

182
00:08:41,435 --> 00:08:42,354
Watch your words!

183
00:08:44,155 --> 00:08:44,995
Li Kuang,

184
00:08:45,474 --> 00:08:46,834
as Rundu's commander,

185
00:08:47,594 --> 00:08:50,435
you point blades
at your women and people.

186
00:08:51,075 --> 00:08:51,915
What's this?

187
00:08:52,634 --> 00:08:53,634
They volunteered.

188
00:08:54,515 --> 00:08:55,555
Their sortie

189
00:08:55,594 --> 00:08:57,355
is to deceive the enemy and buy time.

190
00:08:57,994 --> 00:09:00,435
As the Rundu commander,
I'll lead the charge

191
00:09:01,075 --> 00:09:02,834
and fight to the death
defending this city.

192
00:09:03,474 --> 00:09:04,874
Better die meaningfully

193
00:09:05,275 --> 00:09:06,354
than live in shame.

194
00:09:08,075 --> 00:09:08,915
Volunteered?

195
00:09:11,114 --> 00:09:11,954
Let me ask you.

196
00:09:13,075 --> 00:09:14,594
Are you truly willing?

197
00:09:19,395 --> 00:09:20,874
I... I...

198
00:09:21,555 --> 00:09:22,834
I don't want to die.

199
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,954
I want to live with dignity.

200
00:09:29,834 --> 00:09:31,195
You shouldn't feel ashamed.

201
00:09:31,874 --> 00:09:32,915
Shame belongs to

202
00:09:33,395 --> 00:09:34,634
Commander Li.

203
00:09:39,155 --> 00:09:39,995
Li Kuang.

204
00:09:40,195 --> 00:09:41,275
Did they volunteer

205
00:09:41,714 --> 00:09:43,675
or were they forced to do this?

206
00:09:44,315 --> 00:09:45,634
You know the truth.

207
00:09:46,075 --> 00:09:48,435
Aren't they Rundu's citizens?

208
00:09:49,795 --> 00:09:51,035
As the city's commander,

209
00:09:51,555 --> 00:09:52,395
you make

210
00:09:52,395 --> 00:09:54,634
those you should protect die needlessly.

211
00:09:57,114 --> 00:09:57,954
Swords

212
00:09:58,795 --> 00:10:00,155
are for enemies.

213
00:10:00,994 --> 00:10:02,754
Never against the weak.

214
00:10:05,315 --> 00:10:06,155
Yes.

215
00:10:09,114 --> 00:10:10,354
Never against the weak.

216
00:10:19,795 --> 00:10:20,635
Commander.

217
00:10:28,994 --> 00:10:30,315
You haven't changed.

218
00:10:31,395 --> 00:10:32,315
General Zhang

219
00:10:32,954 --> 00:10:34,915
used a few citizens as bait.

220
00:10:35,954 --> 00:10:37,275
It lacked compassion.

221
00:10:37,954 --> 00:10:39,714
But compared to losing the city,

222
00:10:40,195 --> 00:10:43,594
it was minor.

223
00:10:44,035 --> 00:10:47,195
So, in a crisis, we must
make such a trade-off.

224
00:10:49,435 --> 00:10:50,275
Sir,

225
00:10:50,675 --> 00:10:52,075
but I hold a different view.

226
00:10:52,915 --> 00:10:54,395
I understand General Zhang.

227
00:10:54,795 --> 00:10:55,915
But if it were me,

228
00:10:56,594 --> 00:10:57,714
I would never act this way.

229
00:10:58,275 --> 00:10:59,834
I'd lead the remaining soldiers

230
00:11:00,195 --> 00:11:01,035
to fight the rebels

231
00:11:01,435 --> 00:11:02,915
at the city gates.

232
00:11:03,915 --> 00:11:05,234
The one who wields the sword

233
00:11:05,634 --> 00:11:06,474
must know

234
00:11:06,874 --> 00:11:08,874
whether the blade is meant

235
00:11:09,874 --> 00:11:11,315
for the enemy in front

236
00:11:11,834 --> 00:11:13,435
or the weak behind them.

237
00:11:16,354 --> 00:11:18,195
I will never draw
my sword against the weak.

238
00:11:32,075 --> 00:11:34,555
C-C-Commander Xiao's here? How?

239
00:11:35,675 --> 00:11:36,954
Do you think

240
00:11:37,394 --> 00:11:38,234
it's because of...?

241
00:11:38,234 --> 00:11:39,994
Because of our absence from camp,

242
00:11:40,474 --> 00:11:41,314
he came to punish us?

243
00:11:42,714 --> 00:11:44,795
No, that can't be it.

244
00:11:45,315 --> 00:11:46,474
He seems in good spirits.

245
00:11:47,195 --> 00:11:48,075
He even smiled.

246
00:11:49,234 --> 00:11:50,074
Really?

247
00:11:50,275 --> 00:11:51,234
Absolutely true.

248
00:11:51,874 --> 00:11:55,395
D-D-Don't worry.

249
00:11:55,395 --> 00:11:56,994
S-S-Stop mocking me.

250
00:11:58,474 --> 00:11:59,314
General Fengyun,

251
00:11:59,795 --> 00:12:00,635
how did you get in?

252
00:12:01,234 --> 00:12:02,155
I fought my way through

253
00:12:02,714 --> 00:12:03,675
with my battalion.

254
00:12:05,155 --> 00:12:06,714
Commander Xiao, it must be hard work.

255
00:12:09,795 --> 00:12:10,635
Commander Li,

256
00:12:11,714 --> 00:12:13,354
General Wu'an is my man.

257
00:12:14,114 --> 00:12:15,675
My soldiers' discipline

258
00:12:16,354 --> 00:12:17,435
is my own responsibility.

259
00:12:17,954 --> 00:12:19,354
No outsiders may interfere.

260
00:12:20,354 --> 00:12:21,195
Besides,

261
00:12:22,395 --> 00:12:23,235
he wasn't wrong.

262
00:12:27,275 --> 00:12:29,675
I know I'm the one at fault.

263
00:12:29,714 --> 00:12:31,515
But I'm ready to die defending Rundu.

264
00:12:31,555 --> 00:12:32,634
Already thinking of defeat?

265
00:12:32,994 --> 00:12:35,075
Rundu needs
no cowardly commanders like you.

266
00:12:42,315 --> 00:12:43,474
Warriors fear not death

267
00:12:44,474 --> 00:12:45,994
but wield swords to protect our land

268
00:12:46,834 --> 00:12:47,915
and our people.

269
00:12:56,474 --> 00:12:57,314
Soldiers!

270
00:12:57,634 --> 00:12:58,515
Both we and the Wutuo

271
00:12:58,915 --> 00:12:59,795
lack supplies.

272
00:13:00,354 --> 00:13:01,714
This is a do-or-die battle.

273
00:13:02,195 --> 00:13:04,474
The brave will win.

274
00:13:05,114 --> 00:13:05,954
Besides,

275
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:09,515
General Fengyun's reinforcements
have arrived.

276
00:13:10,795 --> 00:13:12,354
Director Chu of the Ministry of War

277
00:13:12,994 --> 00:13:14,195
has brought us provisions.

278
00:13:15,354 --> 00:13:18,395
Millions of Wei citizens
stand behind us.

279
00:13:19,195 --> 00:13:20,234
As warriors,

280
00:13:20,874 --> 00:13:22,555
we raise swords to protect our land

281
00:13:22,795 --> 00:13:23,714
and our people!

282
00:13:24,754 --> 00:13:25,594
Soldiers!

283
00:13:25,915 --> 00:13:27,075
Will you join me

284
00:13:27,714 --> 00:13:30,035
to fight the enemy outside, repel Wutuo,

285
00:13:30,634 --> 00:13:31,634
and defend Rundu

286
00:13:32,275 --> 00:13:33,435
and Wei?

287
00:13:33,874 --> 00:13:34,754
- Yes!
- Yes!

288
00:13:35,594 --> 00:13:36,434
General Fengyun

289
00:13:37,035 --> 00:13:38,754
and General Wu'an stand with Rundu.

290
00:13:39,395 --> 00:13:40,235
This battle,

291
