419
00:27:41,674 --> 00:27:42,715
were forced by me.

420
00:27:43,354 --> 00:27:44,594
Please don't punish them.

421
00:27:45,194 --> 00:27:46,035
All blame

422
00:27:46,555 --> 00:27:47,795
