452
00:29:41,674 --> 00:29:43,954
You are just you.

453
00:29:44,634 --> 00:29:45,515
You've always been

454
00:29:46,275 --> 00:29:47,634
my tenacious classmate

455
00:29:48,674 --> 00:29:50,154
with unwavering integrity,

456
00:29:52,634 --> 00:29:54,114
the general who defended our borders

457
00:29:55,715 --> 00:29:57,434
without hesitation
even in mortal danger.

458
00:30:00,515 --> 00:30:01,674
After returning from Peidu,

459
00:30:02,594 --> 00:30:03,674
I wanted to apologize

460
00:30:04,874 --> 00:30:06,394
and clarify everything

461
00:30:08,154 --> 00:30:09,114
and then accompany you

462
00:30:10,035 --> 00:30:11,075
to reinforce Rundu.

463
00:30:12,475 --> 00:30:13,315
But by then,

464
00:30:14,194 --> 00:30:15,594
