492
00:31:45,475 --> 00:31:47,674
You're magnanimous, Miss He.

493
00:31:49,275 --> 00:31:50,115
Please forgive me.

494
00:31:53,154 --> 00:31:54,475
I'm generous,

495
00:31:55,075 --> 00:31:56,315
so you're forgiven.

496
00:32:02,434 --> 00:32:03,594
