502
00:32:17,154 --> 00:32:19,034
I investigated the Huayuan Battle.

503
00:32:19,034 --> 00:32:21,235
The seven generals
initially divided into

504
00:32:21,515 --> 00:32:22,555
three groups as planned

505
00:32:23,035 --> 00:32:25,154
to support He Rufei who was
against Wutuo's main army.

506
00:32:25,794 --> 00:32:26,634
But en route,

507
00:32:26,634 --> 00:32:27,995
they all fell into Wutuo ambushes.

508
00:32:28,475 --> 00:32:29,475
All seven perished.

509
00:32:29,914 --> 00:32:31,275
Then He Rufei avenged them

510
00:32:31,755 --> 00:32:33,075
by crushing the Wutuo forces

511
00:32:33,434 --> 00:32:34,674
and driving them from Huayuan.

512
00:32:34,674 --> 00:32:35,874
