515
00:32:41,035 --> 00:32:42,154
No survivors?

516
00:32:42,834 --> 00:32:44,874
He Rufei alone

517
00:32:45,194 --> 00:32:46,235
emerged victorious,

518
00:32:46,674 --> 00:32:47,514
repelling

519
00:32:47,515 --> 00:32:48,914
the formidable Wutuo army?

520
00:32:50,475 --> 00:32:51,475
He Rufei

521
00:32:51,834 --> 00:32:54,315
schemed to conceal his true identity.

522
00:32:54,834 --> 00:32:56,035
He teamed up with Wutuo again

523
00:32:56,434 --> 00:32:57,354
and set the ambush

524
00:32:57,874 --> 00:32:58,914
to kill them indirectly.

525
00:32:59,434 --> 00:33:01,035
Suspecting your survival,

526
00:33:01,914 --> 00:33:03,594
he first used the Wutuo forces to kill

527
00:33:04,235 --> 00:33:05,475
the Seven Tiger Generals.

528
00:33:06,075 --> 00:33:07,594
