537
00:33:25,895 --> 00:33:27,755
or the people of Rundu,

538
00:33:28,315 --> 00:33:29,315
I had to come.

539
00:33:31,914 --> 00:33:32,995
He Rufei prides himself

540
00:33:33,555 --> 00:33:35,354
on manipulating people's minds.

541
00:33:36,394 --> 00:33:38,595
But he never anticipated

542
00:33:39,755 --> 00:33:42,154
that you would risk being charged again

543
00:33:42,874 --> 00:33:44,154
to reinforce Rundu.

544
00:33:48,154 --> 00:33:48,994
By the way,

545
00:33:49,194 --> 00:33:50,434
could you ask Li Kuang

546
00:33:50,594 --> 00:33:52,834
to draft a reinforcement request
for you and Yan He

547
00:33:53,475 --> 00:33:55,275
to prevent those with ulterior motives

548
00:33:56,275 --> 00:33:57,394
from twisting the situation?

549
00:34:00,154 --> 00:34:01,674
By wearing that mask this time,

550
00:34:02,674 --> 00:34:04,674
you've terrified the Wutuo forces.

551
00:34:05,395 --> 00:34:06,915
