with my head held high.

557
00:34:20,754 --> 00:34:21,875
I'll make sure he learns

558
00:34:24,114 --> 00:34:26,955
who the real General Feihong is.

559
00:34:30,355 --> 00:34:31,314
Speaking of which,

560
00:34:32,515 --> 00:34:34,035
since He Rufei and Xu Jingfu

561
00:34:34,274 --> 00:34:35,594
have been colluding for so long,

562
00:34:35,955 --> 00:34:36,835
there must be evidence

563
00:34:37,234 --> 00:34:38,515
of their collaboration.

564
00:34:39,075 --> 00:34:39,955
And that evidence

565
00:34:40,435 --> 00:34:41,314
is in the capital.

566
00:34:41,794 --> 00:34:43,194
So I want to return sooner

567
00:34:43,435 --> 00:34:45,314
to investigate potential leads.

568
00:34:46,475 --> 00:34:48,515
Good. I'll go with you.

